  <tr><td>&nbsp;</td></tr>
  <tr>
    <td align="left" valign="top"><font face="Verdana" size="2">
    Found off a rare spawn named Lord Grimrot In South Karanas. Lord Grimrot spawns in the middle of the Skeleton ruins near the white bridge. This used to be called An Opal Scythe before the patch.<br>
Adds +10SV Poison & Disease<br>
Effect: Vampiric Curse<BR>
Charges: 1</font>
    </td>
  </tr>
  
